0191 - General Farms, Primarily Crop Summary > HWF HOLDCO 1 PTY LTD (formerly HORNSDALE WIND FARM PTY LTD) is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover general farms, primarily crop. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. HWF HOLDCO 1 PTY LTD is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by chief executive officer Duncan John Jewell. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.92 million. Its net loss totalled $1.36 million. HWF HOLDCO 1 PTY LTD forms part of the agriculture, forestry, and fishing industry sector.
